+    "ac_minting": "No new AC minted. Work is tracked by requirement id (R-20-RV / R-20-NV) + TDD test names, per the acceptance.md lock. AC-079 remains unminted and available.",
+    "note": "The phrase HITL-SIGNED was NOT written anywhere by this slice."
